org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.multiobjective

Class MultiobjectiveFitnessEvaluator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.multiobjective.MultiobjectiveFitnessEvaluator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FitnessEvaluator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NSGAFitnessEvaluator

    public abstract class MultiobjectiveFitnessEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
implements FitnessEvaluator
    Basic class for multi-objective fitness evaluations. Provides the interface and some utility methods (non-dominated front extraction, non-dominated sorting and crowding distance assignment).
    Author:
    Martin Pilat
